Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Prominently situated on Rodney Square in the heart of downtown Wilmington,Delaware.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
1100 N. King Street and 1100 N. French Street are two,Class A office buildings containing 517,307 rentable square feet prominently situated on Rodney Square in the heart of downtown Wilmington,Delaware.

This world-class corporate headquarters complex features beautiful architecture and wall and floor coverings with granite and marble accents.  You'll also find common areas with an abundance of natural light and stained glass accents.  Designed by Gensler Architects between 1995 and 1997,they were immediately considered the premier complex in the Wilmington Central Business District upon completion.
